<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ861218-0124 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News:Environmental Systems Co.</HL><DD> 12/18/86</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> ESC WNEWS </IN><DATELINE> ENVIRONMENTAL SYSTEMS CO. (Little Rock, Ark.)  </DATELINE><TEXT>    H. ClayRobinson resigned as vice chairman and a director of thishazardous waste management concern. A company spokesman saidMr. Robinson, 52 years old, resigned to pursue &quot;otherpersonal business opportunities.&quot; Mr. Robinson will remain aconsultant to the company. Environmental Systems, which nowhas 10 directors, said it doesn't currently plan to fill Mr.Robinson's former positions.</TEXT></DOC>